parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wipers can reduce visibility while driving in rainy or snowy conditions, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: wipers need to be hit or tapped to start working
wipers quit in the middle of operation

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or fires, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
Oil leaks can cause engine damage, leading to costly repairs and potentially causing accidents.
Transmission and engine problems can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Accessory failure can cause damage to the engine compartment and potentially lead to fires.
symptoms: Bent or separated metal mounting bracket
hood release cable welded to the fender.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A rusted and separated brake rotor can cause loss of braking performance, leading to extended stopping distances, increased risk of accidents, and potential loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: Loud noise from the passenger front of the vehicle when braking
wheel lock-up when brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty brake pedal can cause the pedal to go to the floor, resulting in loss of braking performance, increased stopping distances, and potential accidents.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
vehicle does not stop when brakes are applied
ABS warning light stays on until brakes are applied suddenly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Moisture ingress into the brake system can cause corrosion, leading to premature wear of brake components, reduced braking performance, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Wheels lock up when brakes are applied
especially after traveling a short distance

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Defective brake calipers and rotors can cause overheating, warping, and excessive wear of brake components, leading to reduced braking performance, increased risk of accidents, and potential loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: frequent replacement of brake pads required.
